{"title":"交通管制I","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":125,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-3151","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p><strong>建设公路</strong></p>\n<p>A城是一个刚刚建立的城市，一共有n个区，其中每个区之间都要建设k个高速公路。由于刚刚建设完成，A城的管理者小Z还没建设高速公路。于是，他向你请教：他一共要建多少座高速公路？</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>共两行</p>\n<p>第一行N</p>\n<p>第二行K</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>共一行，高速公路的条数。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>10</p>\n<p>1</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>55</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>30%的数据保证1≤n≤10，1≤k≤5</p>\n<p>70%的数据保证1≤n≤100,1≤k≤70</p>\n<p>100%的数据保证0≤n≤10<sup>9</sup>，0≤k≤10<sup>9</sup>，（待续…………）</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}